STATE FARM MUTUAL AUTO INSURANCE COMPANY v. W. Vernon COLLINSWORTH et al. No. 5797. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Feb. 11, 1958. Rich & Strong, Salt Lake City, Utah, for appellant. Edwin B. Cannon and A. Wally Sand-ack, Salt Lake City, Utah, for appellee.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellant.
